9 to the standard report recipients a copy of its annual strategic
10 plan prepared in compliance with section 363 of the management and
11 budget act, 1984 PA 431, MCL 18.1363. The plan must include the
12 mission, vision, goals, strategies, and performance measures of the
13 department.
